snippet.title: Ultra Foodmess Trailer
snippet.description: Ultra Foodmess is a competitive party game for up to 4 players in which food characters battle against each other in a variety of crazy and fast-paced modes! Experience the food mess! Call your friends to explode, shoot, swing, push, dodge, destroy and, eventually, ruin your friendship.
